{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"代码分割","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Code_splitting","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>**代码分割（Code splitting）**是将代码划分为可以按需/同时加载的多个 bundles 或组件。</p>\n<p>随着应用程序日趋复杂，或仅是对其进行简单的维护，CSS 和 JavaScripts 文件以及 bundles 的大小都会随之增加，尤其是所包含的第三方库的数量和大小的增长。为了避免下载巨大的文件，可以将脚本拆分为多个较小的文件。当前页面所需的代码能够立即加载，而另外的脚本可以在与页面或应用交互后懒加载（<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Lazy_load\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">lazy loaded (en-US)</a>），页面性能因此提升。虽然代码的总量仍然相同（甚至可能大了几个字节），但是初次加载所需的代码数量减少了。</p>\n<p>代码分割是由 <a href=\"https://webpack.js.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Webpack</a> 和 <a href=\"https://browserify.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Browserify</a> 等打包工具所支持的一项功能，这些打包工具能够创建在运行时动态加载的多个 bundles。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参见","title":"另请参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Bundling</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Performance/Lazy_loading\">Lazy loading</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/HTTP_2\">HTTP/2</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Tree_shaking\">Tree shaking</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"另请参见","id":"另请参见"}],"summary":"**代码分割（Code splitting）**是将代码划分为可以按需/同时加载的多个 bundles 或组件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Code splitting","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"La division du code","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Code splitting (コード分割)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Code splitting (코드분할)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/code_splitting","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/glossary/code_splitting/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary","title":"术语表"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Code_splitting","title":"代码分割"}],"pageTitle":"代码分割 - 术语表 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}